110
00:06:09,750 --> 00:06:11,223
an active Iridium,

111
00:06:11,224 --> 00:06:14,728
and a non-active debris-type
Cosmos satellite

112
00:06:14,729 --> 00:06:17,400
this created a lot of extra debris.

