is about the same as for the ISS,

153
00:08:45,921 --> 00:08:51,318
and the reason is the higher density
of such debris at this altitude.

154
00:08:51,319 --> 00:08:54,759
So these are the values

155
00:08:54,760 --> 00:08:58,628
of the probability of collision for
different objects at different altitudes

156
00:08:58,629 --> 00:08:59,957
and different sizes.
